dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Jerry Bell. May I have your name, please?
Hi Jerry, my name is Rose Phillips.
Nice to meet you, Rose. Could you please provide me with your policy number and date of birth for verification purposes?
Sure, my policy number is three five six two one, and my date of birth is zero three dash one five dash one nine eight seven.
Thank you, Rose. One more thing, could you confirm the make and model of your vehicle for our records?
Of course, I drive a silver two zero one eight Honda Civic.
Great, thank you for providing that information, Rose. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that's all for now. Thank you, Jerry, for your help.
You're welcome, Rose. If you have any more questions in the future, feel free to reach out. Have a wonderful day!
